  %p
    Rubyest meetup is heavily inspired by Barcelona on Rails and London LRUG meetups. 
    We aim similar goals to help people to engage and exchange ruby technology
    and knowledge.

  %h2 Seminar topics
  %p
    Most meetup topics are related to ruby programming, however we welcome other topics
    as long it is interesting for ruby people. You are welcome to make presentation, 
    please email to 
    = link_to 'Priit', 'mailto:priit@gitnation.com'

  %h2 Who is coming
  %p
    We expect to see ruby professionals, beginners and students.

  %h2 Regular schedule
  %p
    Currently we are organizing meetups four times in year. 
    Particularly in January, April, July and October and meetup takes place at
    second week's Thursday starting at 18:30.

